  <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
  <section id="experience">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-num">03 —</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-date">Apr 2020 — Present</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">Senior Backend Engineer</div>
        <div class="timeline-company">Kano Solution · Remote</div>
        <ul class="timeline-points">
          <li>
            <strong>Enterprise ERP Transformation (Project Bagong):</strong> Architected a high-performance Go-based data staging and transformation engine. Implemented automated Balanced Scorecard (BSC) indexing and KPI calculation pipelines using MongoDB Aggregation and distributed cron orchestration, ensuring real-time analytical accuracy across Finance, SCM, and Manufacturing modules.
          </li>
          <li>
            Architected and maintain the backend processing <strong>25,000+ ZIP archives/month</strong> across <strong>128 database shards</strong> with <strong>67 orchestrated background jobs</strong> — maintaining zero critical downtime throughout.
          </li>
          <li>
            Led a team of 3 developers as Technical Lead for Project CRA (Sampoerna) and served as the primary client liaison — delivered the full project within a 6-month timeline.
          </li>
          <li>
            Authored the organization-wide Clean Architecture Blueprint, now standard across all teams — <strong>reduced engineer onboarding time by ~50%</strong>.
          </li>
          <li>
            Upskilled 3 junior developers; all reached independent productivity within 3 months.
          </li>
          <li>
            Maintained 5+ third-party API integrations including SAP ERP, Xendit (fintech), and Shipper (logistics) across concurrent production systems.
          </li>
          <li>
            Led the refactor from a monolithic legacy codebase to modular .NET Core — <strong>reducing deployment cycles from days to hours</strong>.
          </li>
          <li>
            Engineered and maintained core backend services for <strong>Sampoerna</strong>, operating across multi-timezone delivery cycles.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="timeline-stack">
          <span class="stack-tag">C#</span><span class="stack-tag"
            >.NET Core</span
          ><span class="stack-tag">Go</span><span class="stack-tag">SQL Server</span><span class="stack-tag"
            >MongoDB</span
          ><span class="stack-tag">Docker</span><span class="stack-tag"
            >AWS S3</span
          ><span class="stack-tag">SSIS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-date">Oct 2015 — Mar 2020</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">Software Engineer</div>
        <div class="timeline-company">Wiyasa / EACIIT · Remote</div>
        <ul class="timeline-points">
          <li>
            Backend engineer for <strong>Shell's</strong> Well Engineering platform (WEIS) across 3+ regional business units — sustaining high uptime through proactive optimization and monitoring.
          </li>
          <li>
            Built high-performance SAP middleware for <strong>Boston Scientific</strong> (DRMS) and <strong>Biogen</strong> — reducing order-to-ERP cycle from <strong>24 hrs to 5 minutes</strong>, reconciliation errors <strong>-90%</strong>.
          </li>
